{"tid":1961175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國禁3M等美企自中出口醫療用品 美批「一級謀殺」擬採法律行動","createTime":"2020-04-06T15:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T16:00:39.000Z","uid":284592,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e699c98b17df2e9886bf73db904229dd44b025f4","tid":1961175,"uid":284592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"隨著新型冠狀病毒疫情持續升溫，美國醫療安全用品製造商告訴白宮，中國禁止美企從中國出口醫療產品；川普總統的法律顧問5日表示，川普政府正在評估對中國此作法採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n川普連任競選團隊的資深法律顧問詹娜．埃利斯(Jenna Ellis)表示：「根據刑法，此行為堪比謀殺的程度。很多人命垂一線，而當你像中國這樣故意做出有預謀的冷血行為，可被視為一級謀殺。」<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎持續蔓延，3M和漢威公司(Honeywell)要求設在中國的工廠，加快生產N95口罩、防疫手套等防疫個人裝備，但根據一名白宮高級官員，這兩間公司的高層透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">中國政府從1月開始禁止他們出口這些產品</span>。<br />\n<br />\n埃利斯表示，他們考慮的法律行動包括向歐洲人權法院(European Court of Human Rights)申訴，或者透過聯合國共同處理此問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/brother_chui/status/1246954128716091392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrother_chui%2Fstatus%2F1246954128716091392&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lexUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=9af3d0f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrother_chui%2Fstatus%2F1246954128716091392&h=8a488ea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/brother_chui/status/1246954128716091392</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6877057/article-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%a6%813m%e7%ad%89%e7%be%8e%e4%bc%81%e8%87%aa%e4%b8%ad%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e9%86%ab%e7%99%82%e7%94%a8%e5%93%81-%e7%be%8e%e6%89%b9%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%80%e7%b4%9a%e8%ac%80%e6%ae%ba/?ref=%E9%A6%96%E9%A0%81_%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6877057%2Farticle-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e7%25a6%25813m%25e7%25ad%2589%25e7%25be%258e%25e4%25bc%2581%25e8%2587%25aa%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%258f%25a3%25e9%2586%25ab%25e7%2599%2582%25e7%2594%25a8%25e5%2593%2581-%25e7%25be%258e%25e6%2589%25b9%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%2580%25e7%25b4%259a%2